                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>St Thomas</placeName>\n                <date>6' Jany 1851</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>My Dr <addressee>Mr Leeser</addressee></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">It has pleased the Almighty to<lb/> relieve my poor son\n                    <persName>Jacob Benjamin</persName> from this world<lb/> of care &amp; trouble,\n                he died in our midst on the <date>27</date><lb/> Ulta on <date>23d of Tebet</date>\n                last, after a protracted &amp; painful<lb/> illness, his mind was brought to a\n                perfect resignation<lb/> of his makers will. I will feel obliged if you would<lb/>\n                insert the following in the Occident</p>\n            <p>Died at <placeName>St Thomas V I.</placeName> in the <date>23d of Tebet</date>\n                corresponding<lb/> with the <date>27 of December</date> last <persName>Mr J B\n                    Wolff</persName> eldest son of <persName role=\"author\">A<lb/> Wolff</persName>\n                of said <placeName>Island</placeName></p>\n            <table cols=\"2\" rows=\"5\">\n                <row>\n                    <cell>The Bible subscription is up to</cell>\n                    <cell>40—to be bound</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>Occident &amp; Advocate</cell>\n                    <cell>4—</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>Occident</cell>\n                    <cell>1—</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>Advocate</cell>\n                    <cell>1—</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>Prayer Books</cell>\n                    <cell>4 setts to be bound</cell>\n                </row>\n            </table>\n            <p>I expect an augmentation as soon as it is closed<lb/> I will send you a copy of the\n                names of the Subscribers<lb/> &amp; other information.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Previous to the death of my Son he informed<lb/> me that he was\n                indebted to a <add>?</add>\n                <persName>Hill</persName> a Shoemaker</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3w951770/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
